# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .dockerignore - WhatsApp Connector
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Excludes files not needed in Docker build to reduce context size and build time.
#
# PHILOSOPHY:
# - Explicit inclusion is safer than exclusion in monorepos
# - But exclusion is sufficient here since we COPY specific paths in Dockerfile
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Version control
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Dependencies (will be installed fresh in Docker)
node_modules
**/node_modules
pnpm-lock.yaml

# Build artifacts (will be built in Docker)
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
.turbo
.next

# Tests
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.js
**/tests
**/__tests__
coverage
.nyc_output

# Development
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log
logs
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Environment files (secrets should be injected at runtime)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Documentation (not needed at runtime)
*.md
!README.md
docs
**/docs

# CI/CD
.github
.gitlab
.circleci
azure-pipelines.yml
.travis.yml

# Misc
*.bak
*.tmp
.cache
.temp
